  "type": "mcq",
  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">There are <span class=\"italic\">n</span>&nbsp;nonfiction books and 12&nbsp;fiction books on a bookshelf. If one of these books is selected at random, what is the probability of selecting a nonfiction book, in terms&nbsp;of&nbsp;<span class=\"italic\">n</span>&nbsp;?</p>\n",
  "answerOptions": [
